public class AccumuloAggregateDBResultReader<C>
extends Object
implements DBResultReader<Map.Entry<Key,Value>,C>

Accumulo specific DB implementation that delegates to the core Accumulo DB result reader with an injected instance of AggregateCellGroupingDBResultReader to handle cell aggregations over Accumulo records.
